<p>Yusaku and Toru films, especially the Game Trilogy is a huge influence on Cowboy Bebop. From the music, the Bruce Lee style posing for his workouts and swagger. Arrow released it on Blu-ray this year with artwork by the legendary <a href="https://nitter.rawbit.ninja/studiotstella" title="Tony Stella">@studiotstella</a></p>
